  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🫧</strong> <strong>A <i>Whimsical</i> Bubble-Popping Adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into this <strong>incremental clicker/idle hybrid</strong> with <strong>tower defense elements</strong>! Start as a lone bubble-popper, build a formidable cat army, and discover strategic synergies that’ll make your inner cat enthusiast purr with delight.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/6d8ba70529323c620ca4d7a87e9770d8.poster.avif?t=1745797195\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/6d8ba70529323c620ca4d7a87e9770d8.webm?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/6d8ba70529323c620ca4d7a87e9770d8.mp4?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 Gameplay <i>101</i> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Pop bubbles</u></i></strong><i><u> → <strong>hire cats</strong> → <strong>dominate the bubble realm</strong>!</u></i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🖱️ Click:</strong> Build <i>satisfying combos</i> and earn <i>cash</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐈 <strong>Recruit</strong>: Assemble a quirky workforce from <i>lazy paw-swipers</i> to <i>explosive Devilcats.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>📈 Invest</strong>: Unlock <i>upgrades</i>, <i>powers</i>, <i>new cats</i>, and discover new synergies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️ <strong>Explore</strong>: Discover <i>mysterious shrines</i> housing <i>extraordinarily rare </i>cats.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔄 <strong>Ascend</strong>: <i>Prestige</i> with purpose, gaining <u>permanent</u> upgrades and unique abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/20a552ef1125e0b331d9b09a359d849a.poster.avif?t=1745797195\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/20a552ef1125e0b331d9b09a359d849a.webm?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/20a552ef1125e0b331d9b09a359d849a.mp4?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🐾 Meet <i>Byte</i>, The Inspiration! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game's muse spends his days conducting <i>gravity experiments </i>(knocking stuff off counters) or <i>battling his arch-nemesis</i> (the mirror). His fascination with soap bubbles was too adorable to not immortalize in game form!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/ac58de84d75b899ee6ce171c404eac5c.poster.avif?t=1745797195\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/ac58de84d75b899ee6ce171c404eac5c.webm?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/ac58de84d75b899ee6ce171c404eac5c.mp4?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong>🤔 <strong>Choose <i>Your</i> Playstyle</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🧘 Zen Master</strong>: Relax as your cat army handles everything <i>(while silently judging you).</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👹 <strong>Clicker Demon</strong>: Chase <i>x25 combos</i> until your mouse <i>begs</i> for mercy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/2bf84c3d990833d9ee9f24e856d46186.poster.avif?t=1745797195\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/2bf84c3d990833d9ee9f24e856d46186.webm?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/2bf84c3d990833d9ee9f24e856d46186.mp4?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌟 Features That <i>Pop</i> </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐱 <strong>Cats</strong>: <i>Unicats</i>, <i>Devilcats</i>, and more — each with <u>unique</u> abilities and synergies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 <strong>Play Your Way</strong>: <i>Tower defense brainiac</i> or <i>zen bubble ASMR enthusiast</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 <strong>Prestige with Purpose</strong>: Unlock <i><u>game-breaking</u> perks</i>, not just boring +1% bonuses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌐 <strong>Endless Scale</strong>: Expand your map to host <i>thousands</i> of bubbles and cats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏱️ <strong>Replay for Glory</strong>: Try <i>speedrunning </i>milestones after your first playthrough!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>Completionist Heaven</strong>: Over ~400 achievements to <i>hunt</i> and <i>showcase</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/37ef5399e895dda562b5c36abb6ce01a.poster.avif?t=1745797195\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/37ef5399e895dda562b5c36abb6ce01a.webm?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/37ef5399e895dda562b5c36abb6ce01a.mp4?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💖 Crafted With <i>Players</i> In Mind</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔋 <strong>Zero Cash Grabs</strong>: Everything’s included! No ads, no \"gem\" BS — just cats being weird.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍞 <strong>Toasters Welcome</strong>: Runs smoothly even on your laptop from 2001.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💻 <strong>Open-Source Code</strong>: Rip it apart, make a <i>Dog Mode</i>, whatever.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪮 <strong>Authentic Cat Hair</strong>: Byte contributed to development by shedding on my keyboard. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/4de51dc4d29ff235feebf8faa0b45ad7.poster.avif?t=1745797195\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/4de51dc4d29ff235feebf8faa0b45ad7.webm?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499760/extras/4de51dc4d29ff235feebf8faa0b45ad7.mp4?t=1745797195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚔️ Declare <i>War</i> on Bubbles!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Click, strategize, explore, and ascend — the bubble realm awaits your feline army!</strong></i></u></p>",
